\section{Feasibility Study}
\subsection{Economic Feasibility}
The system requires no additional cost since free tools (Java, SQLite) will be used.  

\subsection{Technical Feasibility}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Frontend: Java Swing (for GUI).  
    \item Backend: File System / SQLite database.  
    \item Easily expandable and beginner-friendly.  
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Operational Feasibility}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Simple dashboard with intuitive buttons.  
    \item Easy to learn and use for students.  
\end{itemize}

\section{Main Phases}
\begin{enumerate}
    \item Requirement specification.  
    \item System design (DFD and UML diagrams).  
    \item Implementation in Java.  
    \item Testing and debugging.  
    \item Deployment and report preparation.
    \end{enumerate}
