\section{Conclusion}
The proposed system \textbf{NoteX – Collaborative Learning System} aims to provide a simple, user-friendly, and effective way for students to share and manage their notes. With functionalities such as login, upload, search, download, and delete, the system will significantly improve collaborative learning.  

