    \item Designed the Gantt chart showing project timeline.
    \item Ensured that the cost estimation and scheduling of different phases were properly addressed.
\end{itemize}

\vspace{0.5em}
\textbf{RAHMATUL ISLAM}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Contributed to the Problem Analysis, Literature Review, Methodology, Feasibility Study, System Design, Coding, Testing, and Documentation.
    \item Worked on writing the main body of the project proposal.
    \item Implemented the functional details of the system (login, upload, search, download, delete).
\end{itemize}

\vspace{0.5em}
\textbf{Summary}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{NASHSHA ISLAM:} Mainly focused on project planning and budgeting (≈ 50\% of total work).
    \item \textbf{RAHMATUL ISLAM:} Mainly focused on system development, design, and documentation (≈ 50\% of total work).
\end{itemize}

Thus, the project outcome was achieved successfully by combining the planning expertise of \textbf{NASHSHA ISLAM} with the development and implementation efforts of \textbf{RAHMATUL ISLAM}.


